value.0: Under the direction of Druxus Rhym, these rings are created by the Red Wizards of Thay and are sold in their enclaves across the realms. Cheap and easy to make, this magical protection from certain elements is a huge source of profit for the enclaves.

These magic containers allow you to sell a large number of items to stores, without having to sell each individual item.  The price you receive will be identical the price you would have gotten from selling normally.
